&lt;span class=&#34;token function&#34;&gt;docker&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token function&#34;&gt;ps&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;token parameter variable&#34;&gt;-a&lt;/span&gt;
